Products.SmallFormatDescription: Dare Cold Pressed Iced Coffee Strong Latte
Products.FullDescription: Dare Cold Pressed Iced Coffee Strong Latte
Products.RichDescription:
Dare Cold Brew Strong Latte is carefully crafted using 3 natural ingredients, for a rich, smooth finish.

Dare Cold Brew Coffee tastes unlike anything you've tried before!

Crafted using three natural ingredients, we use 100% Arabica coffee beans, fresh milk and just a dash of raw sugar. The coffee beans are carefully roasted and ground before being infused in cold water, to create a perfectly balanced and full bodied flavour. This premium cold brewed iced coffee is like no other.

The Dare Iced Coffee Cold Brew technique delivers a superior form of coffee extraction, taking the time to infuse the beans in cold filtered water gives the coffee a smoother, richer taste.

Arabica coffee

Only three natural ingredients

Made with fresh milk

Australian Made

Products.RichDescription:
Thank you. We at Pureharvest wish to thank you for purchasing this quality organic product. Please enjoy it.

Pureharvest Organic Oat Milk is a nutritious organic non-dairy milk. It has a light taste that is rich in complex carbohydrates whilst having minimal saturated fat. We use whole organic oats, water and a touch of organic sunflower oil to create a satisfying and nutritious food. This versatile food is an excellent alternative to dairy milk for your breakfast cereal, or in your cooking.

All Natural

At Pureharvest we pride ourselves on using only natural ingredients, free from artificial additives and pesticides.

Taste & Nutrition

In Pureharvest Organic Oat Milk, we believe we have created the best tasting yet natural oat milk available. Oats are known to be a good source of soluble fibre which has been clinically proven to reduce cholesterol if included as part of a low-fat diet.

- Unsweetened

- No Cane Sugar

- 98% Fat-free

- Cholesterol-Free

- Lactose-Free

- Non-Dairy Product

- Suitable For Vegetarians

- No Preservatives

- No Pesticides

- No Herbicides

- Say No to Genetically Altered Products.
